bilingual.source: Delacroix's Liberty Leading the People and Alexandros's Venus de Milo.
bilingual.target: 德拉克洛瓦的《自由引导人民》和亚历山德罗斯的《米洛的维纳斯》。

bilingual.source: You can see the Statue of Liberty.
bilingual.target: 你可以看到自由女神像。

bilingual.source: The statue of liberty is an iconic symbol of freedom.
bilingual.target: 自由雕像是自由的象征。

bilingual.source: He fought for the liberty of his country.
bilingual.target: 他为国家的自由而战斗。

bilingual.source: The Statue of Liberty is a symbol of freedom.
bilingual.target: 自由女神像是自由的象征。

bilingual.source: She values her personal liberty above all else.
bilingual.target: 她最看重的是个人自由。

bilingual.source: Everyone has the right to liberty and security.
bilingual.target: 每个人都有权享有自由和安全。

bilingual.source: The statue is a symbol of liberty and democracy.
bilingual.target: 这座雕像是自由和民主的象征。

bilingual.source: The constitution guarantees liberty to all citizens.
bilingual.target: 宪法保障所有公民的自由。

bilingual.source: The iconicity of the Statue of Liberty represents freedom.
bilingual.target: 自由女神像的象征性代表了自由。

list.abstract: Liberty创建于1947年，位于印度香薰产业中心的班加罗尔市，是印度香薰集团SVAW的旗舰品牌，是印度香知名的老字号及行业领导者，获得ISO 9001：2008国际认证。Liberty从原料选材、香料萃取、手工搓制、封装等各个环节都严格把控，截止2013年已出口50多个国家。

yingyinNormal.en: Times like this, security is more important than liberty. There is a war coming John.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在这种时刻，安全比自由更重要。要开战了，约翰。

yingyinNormal.en: For I have sprung you from life's cruel dungeon, and hereby grant you liberty. Suffer no more.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为我已经把你们从那个地牢里救了出来，给你们自由了！你们的痛苦结束了。

yingyinNormal.en: What are you doing? One nation, under God. Indivisible with liberty and justice for all. I remembered it. The champagne is here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你在干什么？一个国家，在神之下不可分割，全民拥有自由公正（入美国籍时的誓词），我记得是这样背，香槟来了。

yingyinNormal.en: Ever since the Colonists arrived in 1624, New York has been continuously shaped by the waves of immigrants drawn here by the promise of hope, and liberty.
yingyinNormal.zh: 自从 1624 年殖民地居民来到此地，纽约一直塑造了移民浪潮，因为这个地方代表了希望和自由的承诺。

yingyinNormal.en: Where's the Statue of Liberty? Where? Right there. God. I can not see it now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 自由女神在哪里？那里.，现在我看不到了。

yingyinNormal.en: Who's focusing? There's nothing to focus on. It's the Statue of Liberty. Right.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谁在集中？没有什么东西可以集中眼力。是自由女神。对啦。

yingyinNormal.en: We stole the Statue of Liberty, the small one from Las Vegas. And I won't even mention the Eiffel Tower! Also Vegas.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们还偷走了自由女神像，虽然是拉斯维加斯那个迷你版的，还有艾菲尔铁塔！也是拉斯维加斯的

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, kids. Come here. Do you see anything right here? Yeah. It looks like a boat. A boat. Yeah. Right in front of the Statue of Liberty.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗨，小子。到这里来，你在这里看到什么了吗？看起来像一只船。一只船。正好在自由女神前面。

yingyinNormal.en: So, the Statue of Liberty is from France, we have a Ukrainian bakery, and the New York Mets are from all over the world. Nice country you got here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 自由女神像来自法国，我们有一家乌克兰面包店，纽约大都会队的球员来自全世界，你们国家很棒。

yingyinNormal.en: Because it's possible to both enforce our laws. And at the same time, embrace the words on the Statue of Liberty that have welcomed generations of huddled masses to our shores. We can do both.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为完全可以在实施法案的同时，践行自由女神像前的铭言，收容那些世代蜷缩在边境线上的人们，二者可以兼得。

yingyinNormal.en: So why is Erica coming to visit? Because we wanna get to know her better, and thought she's never been to New York, so she wants to see the tourist spots: Statue of Liberty, Empire State Building.
yingyinNormal.zh: 艾瑞卡干吗要来这儿？我们想跟她再熟悉熟悉，还有她没来过纽约，所以她想逛逛那些旅游景点：自由女神像啦，帝国大厦啦…

yingyinNormal.en: I took the liberty of making up some vows for you.
I've taken the liberty of arranging massages for you, followed by an early dinner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在晚餐后我为各位安排了按摩。

yingyinNormal.en: I assumed you might say that. Which is why I've taken the liberty of gathering your team.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我就知道你会这么说，所以我擅自集合了你的团队。

yingyinNormal.en: You know that I'm not at liberty to reveal the asset's genetic makeup. Modified animals are known to be unpredictable.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道我不能随意透露资产的基因成分，改良后的动物是不可预测的。

yingyinNormal.en: Lady Liberty's got her panties in a bunch over this but rightfully so, because this Ramsey has created something interesting.
yingyinNormal.zh: 虽然这如同大海捞针，但我们一定要找到她，因为这个拉姆齐发明了一个有趣的玩意儿。

yingyinNormal.en: Due to, this gag order, I am not at liberty to discuss the terms of the judgment, but suffice to say we are pretty happy today.
yingyinNormal.zh: 由于言论禁止令的缘故，我不能讨论判决的具体条款，但可以说，我们今天非常高兴。

yingyinNormal.en: All right, I've taken the liberty of drafting these workflow charts which outline our various duties and the path we will follow as we develop our ground-breaking new app.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，我已经自作主张起草了这些工作流程图，这里列出了我们形形色色的职务，以及开发这独创程序过程中需遵照的事项。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
